    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
      "price": 22000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
