    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a total blast behind the wheel. Come take a look and see for yourself, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
