    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit with its characteristic high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically flawless; the critical VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced for maximum structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing fresh bushings and factory-spec damping for an uncompromised chassis response. Externally, the factory finish is preserved with ceramic coating, while the interior retains its original Nappa leather integrity without bolster compression. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the discerning purist.",
